      "id": "PopularPost333361",
      "post_content": "Maybe it's just me, but I feel like there are a couple of artworks that are quite creepy, but don't appear to be as much within the modern card frame. It's like the orderly frame can 'de-creep' the art.  \nThis printing would be such a case - I feel like this artwork would be more intimidating in the old frame.  \nLikewise, I imagine [Abomination](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?multiverseid=2084) for example would be less frightening (albeit just as disgusting) in a modern frame.",
      "posted_by": "Mode",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost333361\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_post\">Maybe it's just me, but I feel like there are a couple of artworks that are quite creepy, but don't appear to be as much within the modern card frame.  It's like the orderly frame can 'de-creep' the art.<br/>This printing would be such a case - I feel like this artwork would be more intimidating in the old frame.<br/>Likewise, I imagine <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardid=\"2084\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?multiverseid=2084\">Abomination</a> for example would be less frightening (albeit just as disgusting) in a modern frame.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '333361'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy416\">Mode</span>\r\n                                (8/3/2013 7:07:28 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" s